{"tid":2034114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐以色列大使身亡　華春瑩Twitter貼文哀悼錯字連篇","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:42:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":126,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"8f51b1c125ad4f75ea072089c3deb839302a6d03","tid":2034114,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"中共外交部新聞司司長、發言人華春瑩，日前為猝死的中共駐以色列大使杜偉發英文悼文，不料10字竟有3字錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n中共外交部新聞司司長、發言人華春瑩，日前為猝死的中共駐以色列大使杜偉發英文悼文，不料10字竟有3字錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n5月17日，杜偉突然在官邸猝死，終年58歲。杜偉此前任中共駐烏克蘭大使，今年2月剛轉任中共駐以色列大使。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒稱，杜偉的死因是「身體健康原因」，但具體情況還需核實。<br />\n<br />\n當天，華春瑩在推特上以同事身分發英文悼文：「Deepest <span style=\"color: red;\">condolences </span>to my <span style=\"color: red;\">colleage</span> Ambassador Du Wei to <span style=\"color: red;\">Isreal</span>!」。<br />\n<br />\n該推文發表後，網民發現加上介詞僅僅有10個字的悼文，就有3處錯誤。網民說：「condolences」的用法是給逝者家屬；同事英文是「colleague」，不是「colleage」；以色列的英文為「Israel」，被錯拼為「Isreal」。"},{"pid":"9ea15ba9e013fed4af112c19dd61efd77dea81fe","tid":2034114,"uid":267632,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"百度無翻譯架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25d2deb5b561560873d893eaea4d4670b850007","tid":2034114,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f51b1c125ad4f75ea072089c3deb839302a6d03","tid":2034114,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"中共外交部新聞司司長、發言人華春瑩，日前為猝死的中共駐以色列大使杜偉發英文悼文，不料10字竟有3字錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n中共外交部新聞司司長、發言人華春瑩，日前為猝死的中共駐以色列大使杜偉發英文悼文，不料10字竟有3字錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n5月17日，杜偉突然在官邸猝死，終年58歲。杜偉此前任中共駐烏克蘭大使，今年2月剛轉任中共駐以色列大使。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒稱，杜偉的死因是「身體健康原因」，但具體情況還需核實。<br />\n<br />\n當天，華春瑩在推特上以同事身分發英文悼文：「Deepest <span style=\"color: red;\">condolences </span>to my <span style=\"color: red;\">colleage</span> Ambassador Du Wei to <span style=\"color: red;\">Isreal</span>!」。<br />\n<br />\n該推文發表後，網民發現加上介詞僅僅有10個字的悼文，就有3處錯誤。網民說：「condolences」的用法是給逝者家屬；同事英文是「colleague」，不是「colleage」；以色列的英文為「Israel」，被錯拼為「Isreal」。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?ref=781652376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fref%3D781652376&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3ltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=e766b902\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?ref=781652376</a><br />\n蓋ching 呢個你嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d03898af4521d7421e1fbadc60e3634d27457e9","tid":2034114,"uid":19552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"9ea15ba9e013fed4af112c19dd61efd77dea81fe","tid":2034114,"uid":267632,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"百度無翻譯架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:01:52.000Z","msg":"有開autocorrection都應該即時糾正"},{"pid":"2534b91f9ab2e0bcd8335a5e5c84db585282723c","tid":2034114,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8946fe2238a1d3f2f300dd3e88614afb149848","tid":2034114,"uid":335434,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"9ea15ba9e013fed4af112c19dd61efd77dea81fe","tid":2034114,"uid":267632,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"百度無翻譯架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"人地話晒南京大學英文系畢業架 邊駛靠百度翻譯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文系畢業啲英文都咁撚垃圾 還掂都係翻緊牆點解唔用返Google translate啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8256f0ef1a1958a0a79d67846f4ff399c87a3e58","tid":2034114,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-